417
00:24:09,864 --> 00:24:11,153
I must get to class on time.

418
00:24:13,213 --> 00:24:14,868
How old does he think he is?

419
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:17,049
Acting like he’s been here for 10 years.

420
00:24:17,049 --> 00:24:18,010
I heard that.

421
00:24:18,010 --> 00:24:18,963
