462
00:27:46,076 --> 00:27:46,923
Why?

463
00:27:47,022 --> 00:27:48,289
Wasn’t it smooth?

464
00:27:48,289 --> 00:27:49,786
Our acting was great.

465
00:27:49,900 --> 00:27:51,835
